title: The Boys and The Sea Beast Star Karl Urban Aligns His Famous Characters

media:group.media:title: The Boys and The Sea Beast Star Karl Urban Aligns His Famous Characters
media:group.media:description:
"Listen I don't have high expectations at all." Karl Urban joins us to breakdown his characters and rank them on the classic D&D Character Alignment Chart. From The Lord of the Rings Eomer to the smash hit The Boys William "Billy" Butcher, Karl will decide once and for all just how chaotic they really are...
